                <p><strong>Personal information you disclose to us</strong></p>
                <p><em>We collect personal information that you provide to us.</em></p>
                <p>We collect personal information you voluntarily provide, such as names, phone numbers, email addresses, passwords, and IP addresses, when you register, use our services, or contact us.</p>
